	<main>
		<img width="2500" height="1201" src="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-senegal-mangroves.jpg" class="singlepostthumb wp-post-image" alt="mangroves in Senegal" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-senegal-mangroves.jpg 2500w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-senegal-mangroves-520x250.jpg 520w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-senegal-mangroves-1200x576.jpg 1200w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-senegal-mangroves-768x369.jpg 768w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-senegal-mangroves-1536x738.jpg 1536w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-senegal-mangroves-2048x984.jpg 2048w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-senegal-mangroves-900x432.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /><div class="post-thumbnail-caption">After drought killed a large portion of Senegal’s mangroves, restoration projects funded by international carbon trading have restored ecosystems and economies. But critics counter that the social costs of carbon offset programs can be steep, particularly in Africa. Photo by Nick Fox/Alamy Stock Photo</div>
			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">The Social Cost of Carbon Credits</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Multinational companies funded a US $4.4-million carbon offset project. Senegalese locals did much of the work—and saw almost none of the money.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/jack-thompson/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Jack Thompson</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						July 16, 2024 | 2,700 words, about 13 minutes
					</aside>

					
